dct_title_s: Map of Ramsey and Manomin Counties : and Hennepin east
dct_description_sm: Shows land ownership in Ramsey County, present day Manomin Township in Anoka County, and a portion of Hennepin County, Minnesota.
Includes 17 views and 3 vignettes.; Inset view: St. Paul, Minn., 1867.; Blueprint.; Facsimile, location of original and date of reproduction unknown.
Minnesota County Maps, Plat Books, and Atlases
